                  <p><person role="6" wra-ref="" project-ref="JAIFRP-00221">Miss. Nelson</person> called trying to locate "Dick <span type="underlined">Kajawawa</span>".</p>
				  <p>who owns <span type="underlined">2 dogs</span>.  Dogs are being cared for by</p>
				  <p><person role="6" wra-ref="" project-ref="JAIFRP-00222">Mr. &amp; Mrs. C. J. Howard</person>, 9441 SW 8th Drive but owner is</p>
