				  <p>We checked but no name as above was listed - we</p>
				  <p>asked for a correct spelling.</p>
				  <p><span type="underlined">6/24/1942 10:00P.M</span></p>
				  <p><person role="6" wra-ref="" project-ref="JAIFRP-00221">Miss. Nelson</person> called back = Japanese name is "Dick <span type="underlined">Kajikawa</span>"</p>
				  <p>Family # is 15290 - Evacuated to Jap. Assembly</p>
				  <p>Center, No Portland, from West Side Control Station.</p>
				  <p>Called Assembly Center - <span type="underlined">Sec 4.E - 6 B</span>. Still</p>
				  <p>at the center</p>
				  <p>Called <person role="6" wra-ref="" project-ref="JAIFRP-00221">Miss. Nelson</person> at AT 6421 and advised her</p>
